  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1030">
<l>iṭukkaṇkāl koṉṟiṭa vīḻu maṭuttūṉṟu </l>
<l>nallā ḷilāta kuṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there are none to prop up and maintain a family (in distress), it will fall at the stroke of the axe of misfortune.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
